00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:29,080
Qiushui.

578
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:33,650
I have an opportunity in the NBIS.

579
00:27:34,080 --> 00:27:35,880
I can go to Myanmar

580
00:27:35,900 --> 00:27:36,870
as an ordinary medic.

581
00:27:36,870 --> 00:27:37,670
So,

582
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,130
I hope the organization can approve it.

583
00:27:40,130 --> 00:27:40,930
Moqing,

584
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:43,700
your rank in the NBIS

585
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:46,000
is of vital importance for us to get intelligence

586
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,350
inside the NBIS.

587
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:48,380
Qiushui.

588
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:51,890
Once the Cherry Blossom Project is restarted,

589
00:27:51,890 --> 00:27:54,150
the consequences will be unimaginable.

590
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,710
Our operational capability in Myanmar is limited.

591
00:27:59,710 --> 00:28:00,710
If you go alone,

592
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:02,670
I'll be worried about your safety.

593
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:05,120
You don't need to worry about me.

594
00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:06,000
I won't do anything

595
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,640
beyond my capability.

596
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,030
Okay.

597
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,460
I'll pass it on

598
00:28:11,990 --> 00:28:13,380
to the organization.

599
00:28:13,670 --> 00:28:16,070
You should wait for the superiors to reply.

600
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,210
I request the organization

601
00:28:17,210 --> 00:28:19,010
to let me follow the lead.

602
00:28:19,410 --> 00:28:21,280
Now you have three tasks.

603
00:28:21,310 --> 00:28:21,990
First,

604
00:28:22,210 --> 00:28:24,480
find out if Ou Xiao'an's memory loss is real

605
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,540
as soon as possble.

606
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:27,660
Get as much information as you can about 810

607
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:29,450
and report to the organization in time.

608
00:28:29,450 --> 00:28:30,120
Yes, Ma'am.

609
00:28:30,590 --> 00:28:31,360
Second,

610
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:33,700
help Ou Xiao'an as much as you can

611
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:35,980
until you can confirm his identity.

612
00:28:36,220 --> 00:28:37,640
But under one condition,

613
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:39,510
you can't expose yourself.

614
00:28:39,630 --> 00:28:40,780
Not to the NBIS,

615
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:41,840
nor to Ou Xiao'an.

616
00:28:42,060 --> 00:28:42,780
Yes, Ma'am.

617
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:45,640
The third one is tricky.

618
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:47,810
We found there are several Japanese spies

619
00:28:47,810 --> 00:28:49,330
active in Shapingba.

620
00:28:49,470 --> 00:28:50,720
It's in Chongqing.

621
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:52,400
So it's not convenient for us to take action.

622
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:54,720
I hope you can send soldiers from the NBSI to arrest them,

623
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:56,450
in case they sabotage anythng.

624
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:57,400
Yes, Ma'am.

625
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:59,640
These are the three of them.

626
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,500
We've been watching them for a while.

627
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,900
I'll tell you the details

628
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:06,000
on the day of the operation.

629
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,310
Understood.

630
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:13,360
Waiter, a bottle of wine.

631
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,110
Okay.

632
00:29:16,550 --> 00:29:17,570
Your dishes.

633
00:29:18,430 --> 00:29:19,430
Waiter.

634
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:20,990
My order hasn't come yet.

635
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,070
In a minute.

636
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:23,870
I've wait a long time.

637
00:29:23,870 --> 00:29:24,990
It'll come soon.

638
00:29:34,050 --> 00:29:35,110
How's the food?

639
00:29:35,190 --> 00:29:36,730
Not bad. There are three of them.

640
00:29:36,730 --> 00:29:38,930
The boss, the errand guy and the waiter.

641
00:29:45,660 --> 00:29:46,580
On my command.

642
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:56,160
Move!

643
00:30:30,750 --> 00:30:31,630
Don't move!

644
00:30:36,050 --> 00:30:38,330
Tell me, who else works with you?

645
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:47,730
Tell me!

646
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,200
Okay!

647
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:55,180
I'll tell you!

648
00:30:55,220 --> 00:30:56,040
I'll tell you!

649
00:30:57,830 --> 00:31:01,970
[Zhicheng Elementary School]

650
00:31:04,330 --> 00:31:05,420
[Yongyihang Pharmacy]

651
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:30,400
[Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out]

652
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,640
Jingxian.

653
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:48,900
[Zhicheng Elementary School]

654
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,150
Shaotang.

655
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,090
What are you doing here?

656
00:31:49,090 --> 00:31:50,560
My work at the station is finished.

657
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:52,010
Of course I'm picking you up.

658
00:31:52,010 --> 00:31:52,970
Liar.

659
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:56,080
There is so much work to do. How could you ever finish it?

660
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:57,810
Work is not as important as you.

661
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:03,320
Hello, Ms. Feng.

662
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:05,750
Hello. Go home now.

663
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:12,430
Sometimes...

664
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:16,640
[Zhicheng Elementary School]

665
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:14,040
I envy you.

666
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:16,310
You get to be with those kids.

667
00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:18,390
Jingxian,

668
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:20,670
I'll resign

669
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:22,210
after we defeat the Japanese.

670
00:32:22,210 --> 00:32:24,380
I'll teach nature at your school.

671
00:32:24,530 --> 00:32:25,680
Really?

672
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:26,920
Really.

673
00:32:27,280 --> 00:32:30,080
Do you want me to wait for you after class

674
00:32:30,110 --> 00:32:31,840
so that we can go home together?

675
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:33,820
You're so smart.

676
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,120
Let's go.

677
00:32:38,930 --> 00:32:39,890
Shaotang.

678
00:32:40,470 --> 00:32:42,800
Let me tell you a story about my childhood.

679
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:44,210
Sure.

680
00:32:46,990 --> 00:32:49,180
When I was little, my mother and I

681
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,640
lived in Nanjing.

682
00:32:51,970 --> 00:32:53,100
My father said

683
00:32:53,250 --> 00:32:55,160
he'd come back to us

684
00:32:55,190 --> 00:32:57,790
after they overthrew the Beiyang government.

685
00:32:58,510 --> 00:33:00,570
My mother waited for him all her life.

686
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:02,270
Then,

687
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:04,900
Japanese bombs fell on her head.

688
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:08,380
She couldn't wait for my father to come back.

689
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:10,270
After that,

690
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:12,520
my father took me to Chongqing.

691
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:14,090
And I met...

692
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:24,670
I waited for him for three years.

693
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:27,120
He became a traitor

694
00:33:28,350 --> 00:33:29,870
and he died.

695
00:33:32,160 --> 00:33:33,270
Shaotang,

696
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:35,920
I don't want to wait anymore.

697
00:33:43,330 --> 00:33:44,090
Come here.

698
00:33:58,330 --> 00:33:59,330
Jingxian.

699
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,040
I'm not like him.

700
00:34:03,120 --> 00:34:04,720
I will never lie to you.

701
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:13,199
I promise you

702
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:16,300
our wedding will go on as planned.

703
00:34:16,370 --> 00:34:17,580
And then,

704
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:19,790
you'll be the happiest bride ever.

705
00:34:20,350 --> 00:34:21,670
When we win the war,

706
00:34:21,909 --> 00:34:23,239
if you want me to resign,

707
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:25,170
I'll do it in a heartbeat.

708
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:37,770
Do you want to ask me about Ou Xiao'an?

709
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,280
He's still being interrogated.

710
00:34:42,370 --> 00:34:43,530
But don't worry.

711
00:34:43,810 --> 00:34:45,440
General Wei, Deputy General Wen

712
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:47,210
and your father are all there.

713
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:49,690
He'll get a fair trial.

714
00:34:50,060 --> 00:34:52,449
Shaotang, I'm not asking for fairness.

715
00:34:52,469 --> 00:34:54,550
I just want him to live.

716
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:02,990
Are you mad?

717
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,400
Why would I be mad?

718
00:35:08,140 --> 00:35:09,660
I will do my best

719
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:10,980
to keep him alive.

720
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:12,400
For you.

721
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,720
Take off your glasses.

722
00:35:30,360 --> 00:35:32,290
Have you memorized your identity?

723
00:35:32,870 --> 00:35:35,100
I'm Cai Ziyong, a tea merchant

724
00:35:35,120 --> 00:35:36,320
from Southeast Asia.

725
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,960
Keep it in mind.

726
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:39,900
The ID I gave you

727
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:42,310
is absolutely good, okay?

728
00:35:43,670 --> 00:35:44,550
Okay.

729
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:48,100
Don't make eye contact.

730
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:50,120
Your eyes get tense too easily.

731
00:35:52,210 --> 00:35:53,130
Your luggage.

732
00:35:56,980 --> 00:36:00,240
The files are in the bottom interior compartment of the suitcase.

733
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,940
Take them to Chongqing

734
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:05,640
and give them to Deputy General Wen from the Chongqing Station.

735
00:36:06,160 --> 00:36:08,700
Don't let them out of your sight, okay?

736
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,400
What about you?

737
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,260
You're not coming with me?

738
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:14,090
The one who is buying fruit

739
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:15,520
is one of us.

740
00:36:15,910 --> 00:36:17,640
He'll get on the train with you.

741
00:36:17,790 --> 00:36:21,790
[Wang Sen, Agent of Chongqing Station of the NBIS]

742
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,800
We have people on the train, too.

743
00:36:19,890 --> 00:36:22,300
When you get to Nanjing, take a boat to Chongqing.

744
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:23,740
They will look after you.

745
00:36:26,270 --> 00:36:27,470
I'm gonna go.

746
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:28,780
Relax.

747
00:36:28,810 --> 00:36:30,040
Don't be so nervous.

748
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:32,220
-Okay. -Have a safe trip.

749
00:36:32,220 --> 00:36:33,420
See you in Chongqing.

750
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:22,680
[Platform]

751
00:37:25,200 --> 00:37:27,110
[Shanghai Station]

752
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:07,160
Sit back.

753
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:11,080
Show me your ID and ticket.

754
00:38:19,160 --> 00:38:20,000
Hurry up.

755
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:22,500
Ticket?

756
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,690
Okay, yours?

757
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:30,840
Ticket?

758
00:38:33,890 --> 00:38:34,740
Show me.

759
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,200
Ticket?

760
00:38:45,310 --> 00:38:46,150
ID?

761
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,160
Ticket?

762
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,080
Yours?

763
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:05,930
You're from Singapore.

764
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:10,590
I do tea business.

765
00:39:10,700 --> 00:39:13,160
I came back to Nanjing to visit my relatives.

766
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:15,850
Thank you.

767
00:39:24,250 --> 00:39:25,650
What's in your suitcase?

768
00:39:30,910 --> 00:39:35,510
Clothes and tea.

769
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:36,520
Open it.

770
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:41,980
Hurry up!

771
00:39:48,970 --> 00:39:50,660
Just my clothes.

772
00:40:28,870 --> 00:40:29,970
What are you looking at?

773
00:40:29,970 --> 00:40:30,770
What are you doing?

774
00:40:30,770 --> 00:40:32,030
Now you're hitting me?

775
00:40:32,130 --> 00:40:33,330
Bastard!

776
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:34,810
Why are you hitting me?

777
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:38,630
He hit me first.

778
00:40:38,750 --> 00:40:39,690
Sir.

779
00:40:39,750 --> 00:40:40,670
I'm a good citizen.

780
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:41,820
He started it.

781
00:40:41,870 --> 00:40:42,930
What are you doing?

782
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:44,780
You...

783
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:45,760
He hit me!

784
00:40:45,790 --> 00:40:46,430
Stop!

785
00:40:46,450 --> 00:40:47,450
I...

786
00:40:48,030 --> 00:40:48,790
I'll stop.

787
00:40:48,790 --> 00:40:50,250
Don't let him come near me.

788
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:57,830
Stop!

789
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,540
Stop!

790
00:41:04,050 --> 00:41:04,720
Stop!

791
00:41:06,390 --> 00:41:07,140
Bastard!

792
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,350
Get out!

793
00:42:06,270 --> 00:42:10,070
[Feng's Residence, Chongqing, 1945]

794
00:42:16,420 --> 00:42:17,190
Ms. Wu.

795
00:42:17,650 --> 00:42:19,210
Master, you are back.

796
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,660
Where is Jingxian?

797
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:23,080
She called from a restaurant,

798
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:25,700
said she and Mr. Li wouldn't be back for dinner.

799
00:42:26,210 --> 00:42:27,450
It's late.

800
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,020
What are you doing?

801
00:42:30,600 --> 00:42:33,260
Sir, you're forgetful.

802
00:42:33,290 --> 00:42:35,340
These are Miss and Mr. Li's

803
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,750
engagement invitations.

804
00:42:36,750 --> 00:42:39,010
They're done today. Just delivered.

805
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:41,410
I'll have someone take them to the post office tomorrow.

806
00:42:41,410 --> 00:42:42,820
Except for those who live far away,

807
00:42:42,820 --> 00:42:45,060
the ladies and gentlemen in Chongqing

808
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:46,090
will receive it the day after tomorrow.

809
00:42:46,090 --> 00:42:46,980
No.

810
00:42:48,090 --> 00:42:48,940
You will not mail any of them

811
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:50,270
without my permission.

812
00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:53,670
Do you hear me?

813
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:56,080
Put those away.

814
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:56,960
Okay.

815
00:42:56,980 --> 00:42:57,780
Hurry up.

816
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:01,290
Dad!

817
00:43:01,610 --> 00:43:03,010
What are you yelling about?

818
00:43:03,010 --> 00:43:03,850
You're back.

819
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:05,200
Dad.

820
00:43:05,990 --> 00:43:08,530
Ms. Wu, are those the invitations to my engagement party?

821
00:43:08,530 --> 00:43:09,370
Jingxian.

822
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:11,090
Don't worry about that.

823
00:43:11,190 --> 00:43:12,870
I need to talk to Shaotang.

824
00:43:12,960 --> 00:43:14,360
You go upstairs and rest.

825
00:43:15,870 --> 00:43:18,580
Okay, take your time.

826
00:43:18,600 --> 00:43:19,800
Dad, you should also sleep early.

827
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:20,480
Okay.

828
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:24,410
Sleep early.

829
00:43:30,510 --> 00:43:31,350
Sit.

830
00:43:38,450 --> 00:43:39,640
What's wrong, Dad?
